snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

snippet.title: Laxmi Purana ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ପୁରାଣ - Manabasa Gurubar Puja ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ବହିଗୀତ | Namita Agrawal,Gita Dash
snippet.description:
SIDHARTH MUSIC presents "LAXMI PURANA" (Manabasa Gurubar Bahi Gita)
"ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ପୁରାଣ"  ଓଡ଼ିଶାର ଘରେ ଘରେ ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ନାମରେ ମଧ୍ୟ ଖ୍ୟାତ ।
ମାର୍ଗଶୀର ମାସର ଗୁରୁବାର ଦିନ ଓଡ଼ିଶାର ପ୍ରତି ଘରେ ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀପୂଜା ବା ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ପାଳିତ ହୁଏ ।
ଏହି ସମୟରେ ଧନଧାନ୍ୟ, ବାତ୍ସଲ୍ୟ ଓ ଦୟାକ୍ଷମାର ପ୍ରତିମୂର୍ତ୍ତି ରୂପେ ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କୁ କଳ୍ପନା କରାଯାଇ ଘରର ଶ୍ରୀ, ସମୃଦ୍ଧି, ପରିଷ୍କାର-ପରିଚ୍ଛନ୍ନତା ଆଦି ପ୍ରତି ଦୃଷ୍ଟି ଦିଆଯାଇଥାଏ । ମାର୍ଗଶିର ମାସରେ ପୂଜା ଘରେ ଧାନ ମେଣ୍ଟା ବା "ଧାନବେଣୀ"ରେ ସଜାଯାଇଥାଏ । ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ଓଷା ପୂର୍ବଦିନ ରାତିରେ ଗୃହିଣୀମାନେ ଘରଦ୍ଵାର ଲିପାପୋଛା କରି ଝୋଟିଚିତା ପକାଇଥାନ୍ତି । ଗୁରୁବାର ଦିନ ବଡ଼ିଭୋରରୁ ଉଠି ନାରୀମାନେ ସ୍ନାନାଦି କାର୍ଯ୍ୟ ସାରି ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କ ପୂଜା ଆରମ୍ଭ କରିଥାନ୍ତି । ପିଠାପଣା ଓ ଫଳମୂଳ ଭୋଗ (କଦଳୀ, ଛେନା, ନଡ଼ିଆ, ଗୁଡ଼, ଗୋଲମରିଚ ଓ ଅନ୍ୟାନ୍ୟ ଫଳ ) ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କ ପାଖରେ ଲଗାଯାଏ । ଏଥି ସହିତ ମଣ୍ଡା ପିଠା ତିଆରି କରାଯାଇ ଭୋଗ ଦିଆଯାଇଥାଏ । ବିଭିନ୍ନ ପାଳିରେ ଭିନ୍ନ ଭିନ୍ନ ପିଠାପଣା ପ୍ରସ୍ତୁତ କରି ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କୁ ପାଖରେ ଲାଗି କରାଯାଇଥାଏ । 
-------------------------------------------

Singer : Namita Agrawal,Gita Dash
Lyrics : Balaram Das
Music Director : Bharati Krushna,Saroj Ratha

snippet.title: [HINDI] Semi Finals — CEGC 2025 BGMI Day 3 #cegc  #battlegroundsmobileindia
snippet.description:
The road to the Chennai Esports Global Championship 2025 heats up! Witness India’s finest BGMI squads battle it out in the Semi-Finals, fighting for just a few coveted spots at the Grand LAN Finals in Chennai, India — happening November 14 - 16, 2025.

This is where champions are forged — every drop, rotation, and clutch matters. With ₹ 50 lakh on the line and the pride of representing the region on LAN, only the best will survive the storm.

Welcome to CEGC 2025 BGMI Semi Finals

Today's Schedule:
Map 1 - ERANGEL (Group AxC)
Map 2 - MIRAMAR (Group AxB)
Map 3 - RONDO (Group AxB)
Map 4 - ERANGEL (Group BxC)
Map 5 - MIRAMAR (Group BxC)
Map 6 - ERANGEL (Group AxC)

Group A Teams: HERO XTREME GODLIKE | CINCINNATI KIDS | MADKING ESPORTS | AUTOBOTZ ESPORTS | FS ESPORTS | NONX ESPORTS | WELT ESPORTS | WHY NOT ESPORTS

Group B Teams: TEAM IQOOSOUL | MARCOS ESPORTS | IQOO TEAMTAMILAS | IQOO REVENANT XSPARK | ONEPLUS GODS REIGN | ONEBLADE WILD FANGS | BLITZ ESPORTS | VICTORUS SUMUS

Group C Teams: IQOO ORANGUTAN | VASISTA ESPORTS | IQOO 8BIT | META NINZA ESPORTS | INFINIX TRUE RIPPERS | K9 ESPORTS | VERSATILE | RISING ESPORTS

snippet.description:

Subscribe to the LIONSGATE YouTube Channel for the latest movie trailers, clips, and more: https://bit.ly/2Z6nfym

https://www.facebook.com/michaelmovie
https://x.com/michaelmovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@michaelthemovie
https://www.threads.com/@michaelmovie

#MichaelMovie

MICHAEL is the cinematic portrayal of the life and legacy of one of the most influential artists the world has ever known. The film tells the story of Michael Jackson’s life beyond the music, tracing his journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world. Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.

snippet.title: Nallaru Po Video Song | Dude | Pradeep Ranganathan | @SaiAbhyankkar | Tippu | Keerthiswaran
snippet.description:
Presenting the Video song of 'Nallaru po' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Nallaru po'
Album: Dude

Music Credits:

Composed and produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Singers: Tipu , @SaiAbhyankkar 
Lyricist : Vivek

Mixed & Masterd by @SaiAbhyankkar

Lyric Video: ADFX


Lyrics:

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

snippet.title: Billie Eilish - BIRDS OF A FEATHER (Lyrics Cover) | Pop Mage
snippet.description:
Billie Eilish - BIRDS OF A FEATHER (Lyrics Cover) | Pop Mage

♫ Lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I want you to stay
'Til I'm in the grave
'Til I rot away, dead and buried
'Til I'm in the casket you carry
If you go, I'm goin' too, uh
'Cause it was always you (Alright)
And if I'm turnin' blue, please don't save me
Nothin' left to lose without my baby

[Refrain]
Birds of a feather, we should stick together, I know
I said I'd never think I wasn't better alone
Can't change the weather, might not be forever
But if it's forever, it's even better

[Pre-Chorus]
And I don't know what I'm cryin' for
I don't think I could love you more
It might not be long, but baby, I

[Chorus]
I'll love you 'til the day that I die
'Til the day that I die
'Til the light leaves my eyes
'Til the day that I die

[Verse 2]
I want you to see, hmm
How you look to me, hmm
You wouldn't believe if I told ya
You would keep the compliments I throw ya
But you're so full of shit, uh
Tell me it's a bit, oh
Say you don't see it, your mind's polluted
Say you wanna quit, don't be stupid

[Pre-Chorus]
And I don't know what I'm cryin' for
I don't think I could love you more
Might not be long, but baby, I
Don't wanna say goodbye

[Chorus]
Birds of a feather, we should stick together, I know ('Til the day that I die)
I said I'd never think I wasn't better alone ('Til the light leaves my eyes)
Can't change the weather, might not be forever ('Til the day that I die)
But if it's forever, it's even better

[Post-Chorus]
I knew you in another life
You had that same look in your eyes
I love you, don't act so surprised

© Magic Records 2025

snippet.description:
ଏହି ମାର୍ଗଶିର ମାସ ପ୍ରତ୍ୟେକ ଗୁରୁବାର ସିଦ୍ଧାର୍ଥ ଟିଭି ରେ  ଦେଖନ୍ତୁ ୩O ବର୍ଷ ଧରି ଶୁଣୁଥିବା Namita Agrawal & Gita Dash ଙ୍କ  କାଳଜୟୀ "ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ପୁରାଣ"... ଭୋର୫ଟା , ସକାଳ ୭ଟା ଏବଂ ଅପରାହ୍ନ ୪ଟାରେ..Only on Sidharth TV
-------------------------------------------
SIDHARTH MUSIC presents "LAXMI PURANA" (Manabasa Gurubar Bahi Gita)  (Gurubara Laxmi Purana)
"ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ପୁରାଣ"  ଓଡ଼ିଶାର ଘରେ ଘରେ ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ନାମରେ ମଧ୍ୟ ଖ୍ୟାତ । 
ମାର୍ଗଶୀର ମାସର ଗୁରୁବାର ଦିନ ଓଡ଼ିଶାର ପ୍ରତି ଘରେ ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀପୂଜା ବା ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ପାଳିତ ହୁଏ ।
ଏହି ସମୟରେ ଧନଧାନ୍ୟ, ବାତ୍ସଲ୍ୟ ଓ ଦୟାକ୍ଷମାର ପ୍ରତିମୂର୍ତ୍ତି ରୂପେ ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କୁ କଳ୍ପନା କରାଯାଇ ଘରର ଶ୍ରୀ, ସମୃଦ୍ଧି, ପରିଷ୍କାର-ପରିଚ୍ଛନ୍ନତା ଆଦି ପ୍ରତି ଦୃଷ୍ଟି ଦିଆଯାଇଥାଏ । ମାର୍ଗଶିର ମାସରେ ପୂଜା ଘରେ ଧାନ ମେଣ୍ଟା ବା "ଧାନବେଣୀ"ରେ ସଜାଯାଇଥାଏ । ମାଣବସା ଗୁରୁବାର ଓଷା ପୂର୍ବଦିନ ରାତିରେ ଗୃହିଣୀମାନେ ଘରଦ୍ଵାର ଲିପାପୋଛା କରି ଝୋଟିଚିତା ପକାଇଥାନ୍ତି । ଗୁରୁବାର ଦିନ ବଡ଼ିଭୋରରୁ ଉଠି ନାରୀମାନେ ସ୍ନାନାଦି କାର୍ଯ୍ୟ ସାରି ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କ ପୂଜା ଆରମ୍ଭ କରିଥାନ୍ତି । ପିଠାପଣା ଓ ଫଳମୂଳ ଭୋଗ (କଦଳୀ, ଛେନା, ନଡ଼ିଆ, ଗୁଡ଼, ଗୋଲମରିଚ ଓ ଅନ୍ୟାନ୍ୟ ଫଳ ) ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କ ପାଖରେ ଲଗାଯାଏ । ଏଥି ସହିତ ମଣ୍ଡା ପିଠା ତିଆରି କରାଯାଇ ଭୋଗ ଦିଆଯାଇଥାଏ । ବିଭିନ୍ନ ପାଳିରେ ଭିନ୍ନ ଭିନ୍ନ ପିଠାପଣା ପ୍ରସ୍ତୁତ କରି ଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀଙ୍କୁ ପାଖରେ ଲାଗି କରାଯାଇଥାଏ ।

snippet.title: Kajarwa Jab Karelu | Pramod Premi New Song | ft. Raksha Gupta | New Bhojpuri Song | Bhojpuri Gana
snippet.description:
कजरवा जब करे लू प्रमोद प्रेमी यादव का नया धमाकेदार भोजपुरी गाना है, जिसमें उनके साथ राक्षा गुप्ता नजर आ रही हैं। इस गाने में दिल छू लेने वाली धुन और मस्ती भरे बोल हैं जो श्रोताओं को झूमने पर मजबूर कर देते हैं। नया भोजपुरी गाना सुनने के शौकीनों के लिए यह एक बेहतरीन पेशकश है।

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song Name - Kajarwa Jab Karelu 
Hindi - कजरवा जब करेलु
Singer - Pramod Premi Yadav
Featuring - Raksha Gupta 
Music - Chhotu Banti 
Lyrics - Ravi Yadav 
Composer - Lolu Yadav 
Director - Pawan Pathak & Raunak Raut
Assistant -Meenu Sharma & Vivek Mandal
Editor- Rohan 
Dop - Rahul Yadav

Lyrics:-

जय माता सरस्वती
गीत रवि यादव

सरकल ओढ़निया सीना से
पागल भइनी ओही दिना से (×2)

कारी कारी अंखियां से गोरीया हो, कतल गजब करेलु
कजरवा जब करेलु, कजरवा जब करेलु

अंतरा 1
तोहे देखते पगलइनी, बढ़े लागल दिल में बेचैनी
ए करेजा हो, कसम से हम तोहरे दीवाना भइनी

ओठवा प लिपिस्टिक बा लाले लाले
देखा हमरो बिगड़ले बा हाले हाले

दिलवा के बतिया तू दिलवे से गोरी हो सब करेलु
कजरवा जब करेलु, कजरवा जब करेलु

अंतरा 2
देह दूध से उजर बाटे, दुरही से भभकत बाड़ू
जान भगिया ओकर जगईबु, बनबु जेकर मेहरारू

रवि प्रमोद के जियते मुआवतारू
बावे लहर त कहर मचावतारू

गोरकी बदनिया गोरी हो, सबुनिया डभ करेलु
कजरवा जब करेलु, कजरवा जब करेलु

snippet.title: Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Kajal | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music
snippet.description:
#lovesong #payalkikhanak #anilrawat
Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Kajal | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music


#lovesong #payalkikhanak #anilrawat #bhaigirimusic 





हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

It's Ashes squad selection day in Australia, and it's likely that most cricketing headlines will revolve around who's made the final cut for Perth. Unless you're here on the Gold Coas

After a washout in Canberra, we've seen two pretty high-octane T20Is in Melbourne and Hobart. If Australia were the one who steamrolled India at the MCG courtesy an all-time great T20I spell from Josh Hazlewood, it was the Indian bowlers' turn to set up the win with the ball.

We reaches its end with everything still to play for on the Gold Coast and in Brisbane, come Saturday.

When: Australia v India, 4th T20I, November 6, 2025, 18:15 hrs Local Time, 19:15 hrs AEDT, 13:45 hrs IST

Where: Gold Coast Stadium (Carrara), Gold Coast

What to expect: There will be no talk of weather around this contest except for it being sunny and excellent on the Gold Coast. After 82,000 packed the MCG last week, there'll be a relatively fewer people in attendance here at Carrara, with the capacity at around 20,000 at this boutique venue. But the hype around this being the Indian men's first game here has been massive enough for us to get another full house. There's a bit of an unknown around how the surface will play here but the boundaries aren't the biggest, and there will be potentially a lot of balls flying in the direction of the crowds.

Team News

Australia

With Travis Head having decided to get some Sheffield Shield action in as part of his conditioning and preparation for the Ashes, there's an opening for Mitch Owen to go up top alongside captain Mitch Marsh. The return of Glenn Maxwell will be a major boost in terms of experience and also quality to the middle order, which looks pretty ominous with his addition. It'll be interesting to see if Mahli Beardman gets a nod in what will be an exciting first look at the young fast bowler at this level.

Probable XI:Mitch Marsh (c), Mitch Owen, Josh Inglis (wk), Glenn Maxwell, Tim David, Marcus Stoinis, Matthew Short, Nathan Ellis, Xavier Bartlett, Matthew Kuhnemann, Mahli Beardman/Ben Dwarshius

India

India rung in the changes after the MCG and it worked out well for them in Hobart with Washington Sundar playing a key role with the bat. Though the top order should remain the same as Shubman Gill continues to try and finish this tour on a high with the bat, the middle order should stay the same too with Jitesh Sharma having impressed with his cameo. ind vs aus t20 highlights. india vs australia t20 highlights. India Cricket Match vs Australia Cricket at Carrara, Cricket Stadium Australia at 1:45 pm IST. 

Probable XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Suryakumar Yadav (c), Tilak Varma, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Jitesh Sharma (wk)/Sanju Samson, Shivam Dube, Arshdeep Singh, Varun Chakravarthy, Jasprit Bumrah
